  <summary date="2021-04-20T16:39:58Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Safe Routes to All Schools Act

This bill expands the safe route to school program of the Department of Transportation to high schools. Currently, the program is carried out for the benefit of children in primary and middle schools (schools providing education from kindergarten through eighth grade).</summary>
